Class Room

  • java.lang.Object
    • project.Room

  • public class Room
extends java.lang.Object
    Room is the class that sets up the Room Objects, these objects consist of a roomType, whether or not the resident wants breakfast and the occupancy with regards to children and adults
    Author:
    Brian Archbold
